-- Aladdin Capital Names Innes Global Head of Sales, Company's Web Site Shows
-- Daria Solovieva
-- 2010-06-28T17:08:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/aladdin-capital-names-innes-global-head-of-sales-company-s-web-site-shows.html

          
          
             Aladdin Capital Holdings LLC, an
investment banking and advisory firm, appointed  Keith Innes  to
Global Head of Sales, according to the company’s  website .  
 He is also a senior managing director at the Stamford,
Connecticut-based company, starting today.  
 Innes was the head of marketing at Forum Partners
Investment Management LLC. He previously managed Lehman Brothers
Holdings Inc.’s fixed income Asia operation and became the
managing director of the $2 billion Asian credit risk portfolio,
according to the website said.  
 Innes declined to comment on the phone.  
